specs.Gebruiksinstructie:
Only use this wipe to remove thermal compound from heatsinks, CPUs, GPUs, etc.
Do not use if you are allergic to alcohol.
Do not ingest. Seek medical advice immediately if ingested.
Keep away from children and pets.
Avoid contact with eyes, mouth or open wounds. Rinse with water if contact occurs.
Store at room temperature, keep away from heat and open fire.
Discard in domestic waste, do not flush down the toilet.
